title: RIPHen
description:
Fakewhale invites you to mint in memory of the early HEN days from November 11th (11 am CET) to November 16th (11 pm CET)
Participants can mint on any Tezos platform, using the hashtag RIPHEN at mint time.
No limits on the number of editions, however, we do recommend the price to be between 0.5 xtz and 5 xtz â€” In recognition of the event's celebratory nature, we strive to make it as accessible and inclusive as possible to the whole community.
All artworks that include this hashtag will also be displayed in real-time on a monitor located in the IRL exhibition at the Valuart gallery during this period of time.
